52" target="akztarg">My WoW Profile</a><br>Realm: Eredar<br>Guild Master of: Conspiracy<br><a href="HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/journal2.html?user=228318" target="akztarg">LNC</a><br></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from Eredar</td></tr></table>
