		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.98]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=oberonqa&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p><blockquote><b id="fs8">Quote:</b><hr size="1" />I'm having problems. It won't let me add the -notnl tag.<hr size="1" /></blockquote><br><br>Be sure the path to WoW.exe is inside of quotation marks (example: &quot;C:\World of Warcraft\WoW.exe&quot;)<br><br>The -notnl tag must be placed outside of the qoutation marks.&nbsp;&nbsp;So your shortcut should look something like this:<br><br>&quot;C:\World of Warcraft\WoW.exe&quot; -notnl<br><br>If your shortcut looks something like this:<br><br>C:\World of Warcraft\WoW.exe -notnl<br><br>then it won't work... as there are no quotation marks in the path.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><u>WoW</u><br>-<a href="HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?35583" target="akztarg"> <b>Neocron</b></a>: Night Elf Warrior (Durotan - Outcastz Guild)<br>-<a href="HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?63424" target="akztarg"> <b>Taalin</b></a>: Tauren Shamen (Shadow Council - Unguilded)<br><br><u>FFXI</u><br>-<a href="HTTP://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?77022" target="akztarg"> <b>Neocron</b></a>: San d'Orian Tarutaru BLM60/WHM30 (Gilgamesh Server - KoruptionINC LS)&nbsp;&nbsp;(Retired)<br><br><i>Fear is the mind killer</i></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from Somewhere.... just not sure WHERE</td></tr></table>
